# 💧 Hydrate Happy App
A friendly hydration reminder app that helps you build the habit of drinking enough water every day.

## 🎯 Who It's For
Anyone who forgets to drink water during busy workdays — entrepreneurs, creators, and professionals.

## ✨ Features
- Daily water intake reminders
- Simple, clean interface
- Encourages healthy hydration habits

